      "name": "About Technology",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "THE TECHNOLOGY",
        "heading": "Smart-Zinc™ Technology —\nthe only mouthwash that\neliminates bad breath at its source.",
        "body": "<p>When our two solutions combine in the cup, billions of zinc ions are released. These zinc ions block germs from consuming protein in your saliva — stopping sulfur gas production entirely. Not temporarily. For 24 hours.</p><p>It’s a genuinely different mechanism from every other mouthwash on the market — and it’s protected by multiple patents that no other brand can replicate.</p>",
