        "body": "<p>SmartMouth was never just about fresh breath. From the beginning, our founders believed that oral health is a gateway to overall health — and that a product that genuinely worked could change people’s lives, not just their morning routine.</p><p>The link between oral health and heart disease, diabetes and other systemic conditions is well established. That’s why SmartMouth is built to actually address the root cause — not paper over it.</p>",
